#Virtual Reality


"""The user is effectively immersed in a responsive virtual world.
                                           -Freed Brooks(1999) """

Virtual reality(VR) is a computer generated graphical representation of real or fantasy world. The expierence delivered by this will be very different from 
watching TV at home or going to cinema. The expierence delivered by this would be immersive, engaging and interactive, we can get this immersive experience by using a small 
range of vr displays like CAVE live systems or Head Mounted Display(HMD). Major players in Virtual Reality display's include HTC Vive, Oculus Rift and PlayStation VR (PSVR).
